                                               dkkmPos.*,
                                               kmstp.MaST
                                        FROM   KhuyenMaiPOS kmp
                                               LEFT JOIN CTKhuyenMaiPOS cmp
                                                    ON  cmp.MaDotKhuyenMai = kmp.MaDotKhuyenMai
                                               LEFT JOIN KhuyenMai_SieuThiPOS kmstp
                                                    ON  kmstp.MaDotKhuyenMai = kmp.MaDotKhuyenMai
                                               LEFT JOIN DieuKienKhuyenMaiPOS dkkmPos
                                                    ON  dkkmPos.CTKhuyenMaiID = cmp.CTKhuyenMaiID
                                            WHERE  1 = 1  AND cmp.MaLoaiKhuyenMai = 12
                                                   AND kmp.DaApDung = 1
                                                   AND @NgayHD BETWEEN kmp.TuNgay AND kmp.DenNgay
                                                   AND cmp.GiaTriTongHoaDon <= 76486.800 
                                                   AND kmstp.MaST LIKE 
                                                       CASE kmstp.MaST
                                                            WHEN '0000' THEN '%%'
                                                            ELSE '2210'
                                                       END
                                            ORDER BY
                                                   kmp.STT ASC,
                                                   cmp.STT ASC
